Comedy Nights With Kapil
Season 1 Ep. 55
Released: 16/02/14
Running time: 01:07:09

On the occasion of Pinky Bua's wedding, Kapil does a wonderful arrangement of entertainment for the Fufaji. With this Kapil also starts his wisecracks and one-liners, having the audience in splits. Indian Idol fame, Abhijeet Sawant and the Jhalak girl, Loren show their presence with some sizzling and funny performances. Later, the guest of the night, Farhan Akhtar and Vidhya Balan join the stage with the host Kapil, to promote their upcoming movie, Shadi Ke Side Effect, but get disturbed by Kapil's weird family members. Further, Farhan and Vidya share their side on Shadi Ke Side Effect. Watch the entire episode, to know what happened with Pinky Bua's marriage.
